casebody.data:
No. 109,

Orig.

Oklahoma et al. v. New Mexico.

Interim report of the Special Master received and ordered filed. Motion of the Special Master for allowance of compensation and reimbursement of expenses granted, and the Special Master is awarded $22,200.83, one-third to be paid by each party. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 489 U. S. 1005.]
